    "body": "### Spark-context\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/apache/spark/commit/2e1467f748\r\n\r\n### What changes were proposed in SPARK pull request?\r\n\r\nSimilar to the refactor done `PythonArrowOutput` in [SPARK-29317](40485f4), this PR factors the Arrow input code path out as `PythonArrowInput`\r\n\r\n### Why are the changes needed in Spark?\r\n\r\nCode-refactor\r\n\r\n\r\n### Does this PR introduce _any_ user-facing change?\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\n### Why it might affect RAPIDS?\r\n\r\nCurrently, We define a trait [GpuPythonArrowOutput](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/branch-22.08/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/rapids/execution/python/GpuArrowEvalPythonExec.scala#L251) which is used\r\nin declaring class [GpuArrowPythonRunner](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/branch-22.08/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/rapids/execution/python/GpuArrowEvalPythonExec.scala#L369)\r\n\r\n\r\nWe will need to change `GpuArrowPythonRunner` to be aware of the two traits\r\n\r\n```\r\nclass GpuArrowPythonRunner(\r\n\r\n) with GpuPythonArrowInput GpuPythonArrowOutput { }\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Impact on Testing?\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\n### Requires Doc update?\r\n\r\nNo",
